data.description: Welcome home to 725 Holderness Ct and Granite Hill! This better than new home has been immaculately maintained and has tons of upgrades! From the minute you walk in the door you will feel the warm and inviting features of this amazing home. The Richfield plan by Keystone homes features one level open floor plan,  4 bedrooms, 2 bathroom, 1,973 Sq. Ft. LVP in all common areas, large open foyer with office/study as you enter, Gourmet kitchen with custom cabinets, large island, and quartz counter tops with backsplash, recessed & pendant lighting, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, thermostat radiant roof board , owner bath with granite countertop, garden tub and tile surround, walk in shower with glass door and dual vanities. oil rubbed bronze fixtures, fenced yard, oversized corner lot for extra space and privacy, large patio perfect for entertaining or relaxing after a long day at work, sprinkler system,  2 car garage, tons of natural light and so many more custom touches! You will not find a better price for such an amazing home and upgrades as this home has!
